  "text": "This constitutes the first construction of CAP representations on higher degree covering groups. In Section 14, we provide evidence based on the dimension equation that t(π) > 0 holds if π is generic. As noted in [CITATION_1] Section 15] , this choice induces a well-defined W -equivariant lifting",
